    "Name": "Hachiwara",
    "Details": "The Hachiwara's main armament is its experimental Vibroblade. This is backed up by an Ultra  10 Autocannon, as well as two ER medium lasers for medium-long range attacks and four M-Pods for additional close-range power.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Melee Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Left Upper</color>",
